  "title": "Assistant Programme Executive (Serangoon)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a compassionate and enthusiastic team player to join us as an Assistant Programme Executive at Active Ageing Centre @ Serangoon. The Assistant Programme Executive assists with the centre activities and clients at the centre</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Plan and prepare monthly activities schedule for clients.</p>\n<p>- Engage with the clients during the activities.</p>\n<p>- Pack and distribute food ration packages.</p>\n<p>- Assess clients’ need and make necessary referrals to appropriate agencies and/or various care services.</p>\n<p>- Manage and maintain all necessary documentations and paperwork of clients’ data and centre activities.</p>\n<p>- Maintain the general cleanliness of the centre.</p>\n<p>- Assist the centre manager on any other ad-hoc duties.</p>",
